text: Anton Eisgruber (1 November 1912 - 3 July 1994) was a German skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1994 deaths Category:German male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Germany Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Garmisch-Partenkirchen
